Common.SpaceDescription.Common.Text: Spec Suite with 2 offices, interior conference room, private restroom, break room and open office area.
5 exterior offices, exterior conference room, private restroom, break room, reception and open office area

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: Located in the 500,000 SF Corporate Center near downtown Golden.  Location offers convenient accessibility to Golden, the foothills, downtown Denver, I-70, 6th Avenue and C-470.  Additional amenities include private entrance, 24/7 HVAC control and upgraded tenant finishes.

The property is located directly across from the Coors Brewery.  It is just two (2) minutes to 6th Avenue Freeway, Hwy 93 or Hwy 58, 20 minutes to Downtown Denver, 25 minutes to Boulder, and 15 minutes to Evergreen exit.  Denver International Airport shuttle service is available 24 hours daily. Abundant free covered parking available. In Downtown Golden with numerous retail amenities in building and within easy walking distance. Showers and lockers in building. Great views and easy access.
